â€¢ Have been diagnosed with: A psychological anxiety disorder, Psychiatric disorders (Bipolar disorder, Depression), Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder and Epilepsy.
- Are taking any chronic medication for anxiety or mood stabilizing
- Are pregnant or lactating
